  data/notebook/YYYY-MM-DD.jsonl and data/timeline/YYYY-MM-DD.jsonl.
- Reading scans all daily files (sorted by date) for full history.
- Backward compatible: legacy single-file notebook.jsonl and
  timeline.jsonl are still read if present.

